{"tid":2421430,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳孟達罹患肝癌 田雞證實星爺致電關心：佢想睇吓有冇嘢幫到手","createTime":"2021-02-24T13:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T07:33:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e4db32faeee68a0ddfc3fe047381dea2190a7e0e","tid":2421430,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"今年70歲的吳孟達（達哥）近年屢傳病重，其好友田啟文（田雞）日前證實達哥不幸罹患肝癌惡疾，兩個月前做過切除手術，現時留院接受化療。達哥患病消息傳出，外界紛紛致電田啟文（田雞）關心其病況，其中一個更是達哥昔日在電影中的「戰友」周星馳（星爺），有指星爺一看到新聞，即時致電田雞詢問，但由於田雞當晚早瞓，因此熄了電話沒有聯繫，田雞今日回覆《蘋果》時，證實曾和星爺通過電話，他說：「星爺之前係有打畀我問吓達哥近況，關心吓佢，睇吓有冇嘢幫到手。」田雞亦表示未有聽過達哥在經濟上出現任何問題，又指星爺一向很關心身邊朋友，只是平時為人習慣低調。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210224/FRZ6CXJCZVBQJCIA6O6FM3PSFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210224%2FFRZ6CXJCZVBQJCIA6O6FM3PSFM%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=53e7bcd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210224%2FFRZ6CXJCZVBQJCIA6O6FM3PSFM%2F&h=bffb52ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210224/FRZ6CXJCZVBQJCIA6O6FM3PSFM/</a>"},{"pid":"b7bb74a0ef36991687ba28589f7495d7c3c740a7","tid":2421430,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hd0NHhU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhd0NHhU.gif&h=aaa589e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dfd70e5f3cd4841f5dfe9ab8aaf50702cb2ccd6","tid":2421430,"uid":165925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0685553e3fc4b4e490f7992876854c3b2d3220","tid":2421430,"uid":129619,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"係咪想搵佢拍戲咋?"},{"pid":"b48196fa0a1174c9212b783dd1144fa0760e6dcf","tid":24